scripts/tools.ua: "# this takes the input vector from a flat array and shapes it to the correct size\nParseStdio ← ↯∞_30⋕⊜□⊸≠@ &sc\n\n# this takes the matrix and and returns a flat matrix out of it\n# this also prints out to the std\nFlatMatrixOut ← &p@ ≡(&pf &pf@ )♭\n\n# this is for getting the keys for the args\nGetkeys   ← ≡(⊢ ⊜□ ⊸≠@= °□)↘1&args\nGetvalues ← ≡(⊣ ⊜□ ⊸≠@= °□)↘1&args\nGetArgs   ← map Getkeys Getvalues\n\n# id,year,month,day,hour,minute,duration_minutes,priority,category_id,deadline_year,deadline_month,deadline_day,deadline_hour,deadline_minute,frequency,interval,until_year,until_month,until_day,until_hour,until_minute,by_day_mask,by_month_mask,by_monthday_mask,by_hour_mask,by_minute_mask,by_second_mask,count,is_mutable,wkst\n# this is a list of functions that are used to make the dev of passes less bad\n\nIdIndex              ← 0\nYearIndex            ← 1\nMonthIndex           ← 2\nDayIndex             ← 3\nHourIndex            ← 4\nMinuteIndex          ← 5\nDurationMinutesIndex ← 6\nPriorityIndex        ← 7\nCategoryIdIndex      ← 8\nDeadlineYearIndex    ← 9\nDeadlineMonthIndex   ← 10\nDeadlineDayIndex     ← 11\nDeadlineHourIndex    ← 12\nDeadlineMinuteIndex  ← 13\nFrequencyIndex       ← 14\nIntervalIndex        ← 15\nUntilYearIndex       ← 16\nUntilMonthIndex      ← 17\nUntilDayIndex        ← 18\nUntilHourIndex       ← 19\nUntilMinuteIndex     ← 20\nByDayMaskIndex       ← 21\nByMonthMaskIndex     ← 22\nByMonthdayMaskIndex  ← 23\nByHourMaskIndex      ← 24\nByMinuteMaskIndex    ← 25\nBySecondMaskIndex    ← 26\nCountIndex           ← 27\nIsMutableIndex       ← 28\nWkstIndex            ← 29\n\n\nGetImmutableRows = ▽¬≡⊡IsMutableIndex⟜∘\nGetRowsWithRruls = ▽ ≡>1 ≡⊡FrequencyIndex⟜∘\nGetFutureRows =   ≡(/+>(↙4datetime now) (↘1↙MinuteIndex))"

